 vnd <instruction>prott es chuell</instruction>
 <instruction>spalt . es enczway an dem hawpt</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>rawmm mit einem <tool en="skewer" commodity="Q1323569">holcz</tool> die <ingredient commodity="Q107246809" en="suckling pig skin">hawtt</ingredient> von dem <ingredient commodity="Q107246807" en="suckling pig meat">fleisch</ingredient></instruction>
 So <instruction>nym denn das vorige vnd drew herte . <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> vnd zway waiche <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> vnd schon <ingredient en="bread" commodity="Q7802">prott</ingredient> <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">Saffran</ingredient> <ingredient en="pepper" commodity="Q3143131">pheffer</ingredient> <ingredient en="table salt" commodity="Q11254">salcz</ingredient></instruction>
 . <instruction>hakch das chlain</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>tuee gesnitten <ingredient en="bacon" commodity="Q11106">spekch</ingredient> darczu</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>full das <ingredient en="suckling pig" commodity="Q23015">vearlein</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>stozz es an ainen <tool en="spit" commodity="Q20181361">spis</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>betwinge die <ingredient commodity="Q107246810" en="suckling pig trotters">fuezz</ingredient> vmb den <tool en="spit" commodity="Q20181361">spis</tool></instruction>
 <instruction>prott es</instruction>
